728314f-b.text:
(1)
Amboy Road, at the N.E. corner of Bethel Ave., showing the Bethel Methodist Episcopal Church. It stands within Bethel
Cemetery. The view is westward.
1924.
P.L. Sperr.

(2)
A view of the church from the opposite direction.
1924.
P.L. Sperr.

(3)
The same, another view.
P.L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS.  1925.
